      "range": "9463-9520",
      "markText": "没想到父亲很快就汇来了钱。二百元整。电汇。汇单的附言条上，歪歪扭扭地写着几个错别字：“不勾（够），久（就）来电。”",
      "totalCount": 2565,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44215769&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=9463&rangeEnd=9520",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5932a1072a2add9c59b123?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=9463&rangeEnd=9520"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44215769_4_8337-8426",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "8337-8426",
      "markText": "老大！你太自私了！你心中根本没有父母！根本没有弟弟妹妹！你只想到你自己！你一心奔你个人的前程吧！就算我白养大你！就算我没你这个儿子！有朝一日你当了工程师！我也再不会认你这个儿子！",
      "totalCount": 2550,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44215769&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8337&rangeEnd=8426",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5932a1072a2add9c59b123?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8337&rangeEnd=8426"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44215769_4_2183-2280",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2183-2280",
      "markText": "中国的贫穷家庭的主妇，对困苦生活的适应力和忍耐力是极可敬的。她们凭一种本能对未来充满憧憬。虽然这憧憬是朦胧的，盲目的，带有浪漫的主观色彩的。期望孩子长大成人后都有出息，是她们这种憧憬的萌发基础。",
      "totalCount": 2472,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44215769&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2183&rangeEnd=2280",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5932a1072a2add9c59b123?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2183&rangeEnd=2280"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44215769_4_456-504",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "456-504",
      "markText": "小时候，父亲在我心目中，是严厉的一家之主，绝对权威，靠出卖体力供我吃穿的人，恩人，令我惧怕的人。",
      "totalCount": 2240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44215769&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=456&rangeEnd=504",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5932a1072a2add9c59b123?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=456&rangeEnd=504"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44215769_4_9905-9993",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "9905-9993",
      "markText": "我觉得衣兜里的两叠钱沉甸甸的，沉得像两大块铅。我觉得我的心灵那么肮脏，我的人格那么卑下，我的动机那么可耻。我恨不得将我这颗肮脏的心从胸膛内呕吐出来，践踏个稀巴烂，践踏到泥土中。",
      "totalCount": 2058,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44215769&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=9905&rangeEnd=9993",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5932a1072a2add9c59b123?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=9905&rangeEnd=9993"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44215769_5_4466-4511",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4466-4511",
      "markText": "父亲的性格也变了，变成一个通情达理的，事事处处、家里家外都很善于忍让的毫无脾气的老头子了。",
      "totalCount": 1848,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44215769&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4466&rangeEnd=4511",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5932a1072a2add9c59b123?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4466&rangeEnd=4511"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44215769_5_3701-3712",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3701-3712",
      "markText": "生活，到底是很厉害的。",
      "totalCount": 1605,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44215769&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3701&rangeEnd=3712",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5932a1072a2add9c59b123?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3701&rangeEnd=3712"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44215769_5_13845-13920",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "13845-13920",
      "markText": "望着远处的铁路讯号灯，我心中默默地说：“爸爸，爸爸，我爱你！我永远不忘我是你的儿子，永远不耻于是你的儿子！爸爸，爸爸，我一定要把你再接到北京来！……”",
      "totalCount": 1568,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44215769&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=13845&rangeEnd=13920",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5932a1072a2add9c59b123?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=13845&rangeEnd=13920"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44215769_4_677-725",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "677-725",
      "markText": "全家七口人高效率的消化系统，仅靠吮咂一个三级抹灰工的汗水。用母亲的话说，全家天天都在“吃”父亲。",
      "totalCount": 1554,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44215769&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=677&rangeEnd=725",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5932a1072a2add9c59b123?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=677&rangeEnd=725"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44215769_19_7335-7381",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "7335-7381",
      "markText": "一些人并不仅仅满足于自己富起来，还时时诅咒别人仍在穷着。因别人的倒运或公开或暗地里幸灾乐祸。",
      "totalCount": 1476,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44215769&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=7335&rangeEnd=7381",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5932a1072a2add9c59b123?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=7335&rangeEnd=7381"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44215769_4_4891-4939",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4891-4939",
      "markText": "父亲侧过脸，低下头，不再吼什么。许久，父亲长叹了一声，那是从心底发出的沉重负荷下泄了气似的长叹。",
      "totalCount": 1470,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44215769&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4891&rangeEnd=4939",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5932a1072a2add9c59b123?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4891&rangeEnd=4939"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44215769_4_2635-2687",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2635-2687",
      "markText": "我第一次发现，父亲脸上呈现出一种真实的慈祥、一种由衷的喜悦、一种殷切的期望、一种欣慰、一种光彩、一种爱。",
      "totalCount": 1320,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44215769&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2635&rangeEnd=2687",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5932a1072a2add9c59b123?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2635&rangeEnd=2687"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44215769_4_1870-1913",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1870-1913",
      "markText": "父亲从来也没对我表示过歉意。因为他从来也没将他打我那一耳光和我以后的口吃联系在一起……",
      "totalCount": 1300,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44215769&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1870&rangeEnd=1913",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5932a1072a2add9c59b123?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1870&rangeEnd=1913"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44215769_20_24750-24803",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "24750-24803",
      "markText": "山口那儿，不知是谁草草垒起三个土坟，有一个女人和一个少年行祭。雪地上，两行脚印，来自遥远而又遥远的方向……",
      "totalCount": 1155,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44215769&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=24750&rangeEnd=24803",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5932a1072a2add9c59b123?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=24750&rangeEnd=24803"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44215769_4_6874-6916",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6874-6916",
      "markText": "而穷困之所以该诅咒，不只因为它造成物质方面的债务，更因为它造成精神上和情感上的债务。",
      "totalCount": 1110,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44215769&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6874&rangeEnd=6916",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5932a1072a2add9c59b123?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6874&rangeEnd=6916"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44215769_10_16806-16829",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "16806-16829",
